      "lineNumber": 70651,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「しかし、そんなすごい技術達も、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"However, even those amazing technologies,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70652,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　現代では扱える人間はごくわずか、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " only a very few people in the present day can handle them,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70653,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その人間にしたって断片的な知識しかない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and even those people have only fragmented knowledge.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70654,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「本来は魔軍に対抗する為の技術だったのに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Originally, it was technology meant to counter the demon army,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70655,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　今ではすっかり失われて久しい……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " but now it has long been completely lost...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70656,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そんなロストテクノロジーが今、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Such lost technology now,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70657,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　長い時を経て人類勝利の為に復活……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " after a long time, is being revived for humanity's victory...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70658,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うーん、なかなか熱い展開なんじゃないかしら」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm, isn't that quite an exciting development?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70659,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「M・M・ルーンとフリークお爺ちゃんも、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"M. M. Rune and Grandpa Freak,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70660,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　草場の陰でにっこりしてることでしょう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " must be smiling peacefully from their graves.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70661,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そして遂に、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And finally,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70662,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　ランス様のお城は空を飛ぶに至ったのでーす！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Lord Rance's castle has come to fly in the sky!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70663,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「うんうん、お城と言えば空を飛んでなんぼよねー」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Yep, yep, castles are meant to fly in the sky, after all.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70664,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これからランス城はどうなるのかしら。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I wonder what will happen to Rance Castle from now on."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70665,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　乞うご期待ってところね！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Look forward to it!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70666,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ではまた！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well then, see you again!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70667,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人と魔王の話！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"A story about the Demon Lords and Demon Kings!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70668,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はーい！　めちゃんこ重要な設定の話するよー！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hi there! I'm going to talk about a super important setting!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70669,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　水飴あげるから、あなたもおいでー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I'll give you some syrup candy, so come along, too!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70670,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そもそも魔王ってなんじゃらほい、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"First of all, what exactly is a Demon King,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70671,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そーんなあなたにも丁寧に説明するヌヌハラよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I'll carefully explain it even to people like you,\" said Nunuhara."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70672,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔王ってつまり、世界を破滅へ導く人間の敵、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The Demon King basically is the enemy of humans who leads the world to ruin,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70673,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その上とんでもなーく強いっていう……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and furthermore is incredibly strong..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70674,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　まあ字面から想像した通りで概ねオーケ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Well, it's roughly as you imagine just from the term.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70675,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ほんでもって魔人というのは、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"And then, a Demon Lord is"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70676,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その魔王に血を分け与えられた、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " someone who has been given a share of the Demon King's blood,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70677,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　とんでもなく強い魔王の部下ね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " a subordinate of the Demon King who is incredibly strong.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70678,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔人の一体だけで国が一つ潰せるほどに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Just one of these Demon Lords can crush an entire country,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70679,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　とんでもなーーく強いのが魔人よ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " that's how unbelievably strong a Demon Lord is.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70680,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「これは全部24体作れると言われてるわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It is said that a total of 24 of them can be created.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70681,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いつもいつでも、魔王魔人は人間の敵……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Always, Demon Kings and Demon Lords are enemies of humans..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70682,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　というより本来は強さに差がありすぎて、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " or rather, originally there is such a huge difference in strength that"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70683,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　人間が支配されるのが当然って感じね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " it feels natural that humans are dominated.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70684,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「こんなやべー奴らが、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"If such dangerous guys"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70685,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　もしも人間界に攻め込んできたら、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " were to invade the human world,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70686,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　超々やべーよねーってずっと言われてきたわ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " it has always been said that it would be incredibly terrible.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70687,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さてさて、今作のランス10では、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now then, in this work, Rance 10,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70688,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　どうなることかしら……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I wonder what will happen...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70689,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ねーねー、ところであなたは",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hey, hey, by the way, who do you"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70690,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人と言えば誰が好き？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " like when it comes to Demon Lords?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70691,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「え、私は誰かって？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Huh, who do I like?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70692,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「全員好き！！！！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I like them all!!!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70693,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「キャー！　ホー様素敵ー！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Kyaa! Lady Hornet is wonderful!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70694,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「というわけでホーネット様の説明よ！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So, here's an explanation about Lady Hornet!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70695,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「魔物界のプリンセス！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The princess of the monster world!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70696,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それが満を持して！　遂に！　今！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"She is finally, at long last, now making her debut!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70697,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　正史に登場！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Making her appearance in the official history!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70698,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「という感じかしら！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Something like that!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70699,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「いやー、21年待ったわこのときを……",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Wow, I've waited 21 years for this moment..."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70700,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　なーんてあなたもいるんでしょうね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " I'm sure some of you feel the same.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70701,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「さて。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Now then."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70702,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　元々、魔物界を統一していた魔王ガイ、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " The Demon King Guy, who originally unified the monster world,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70703,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その方の一人娘であるホーネット様」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " and his only daughter, Lady Hornet."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70704,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「説明を読んでもらえれば分かるけど、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"As you can understand from the explanation,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70705,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔人ホーネット様は簡単に言えば、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " Demon Lord Hornet, simply put,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70706,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　魔物界のプリンセスに当たるのかしら？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": " could be considered the princess of the monster world, right?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70707,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「彼女の目的は父である魔王ガイの",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Her goal is to carry on the will of her father, the Demon King Guy."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70708,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　遺志を継ぐこと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70709,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「新たな魔王となることの出来る美樹ちゃん、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That Miki-chan, who can become the new Demon King,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70710,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　リトルプリンセスに魔王になってもらうこと」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\" she wants the little princess to become the Demon King.\""
    }
  ]
}

